==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: hăo jiŭ chén wèng dĭ
===Etymology===
Literally: The best wine is at the bottom of the jug.
===Proverb===
'''[[好]][[酒]][[沉]][[甕]][[底]]'''
# The best is saved for last; It ain't over until the fat lady sings.

===Alternate forms===
[[好酒沉瓮底]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

